{
  "plan": "Round 1 begins. Initiative order: Norn (13), Gibbering Mouther (12), Ghoul (11). All start alive and have full HP. Norn acts first. The ghouls are hidden in cells but now emerge to attack. No actions have yet been taken this round.",
  "narration": "The echoing corridor of the Gaol stretches before you, its cold stone walls marked by the faded stains of long-past torment. The air is thick with the distant moans and flickering shadows of restless spirits. Suddenly, a guttural snarl shatters the eerie silence as a ghoul bursts from a nearby cell, eyes blazing with hunger and claws ready to rend. From the darkness near the farthest cell, a writhing mass of eyes and mouths bubbles grotesquely—the gibbering mouther sways in maddening frenzy, its ceaseless babble filling the hallway with unsettling whispers.\n\nYour heart pounds as you ready yourself, steel gripped tight, eyes locking onto the advancing horrors. The foul smell of decay and madness hangs heavy in the air, a deadly dance beginning in the stifling prison corridor.\n\nYou have the initiative. What will you do, Norn?",
  "combat_round": 1,
  "actions": []
}

{
  "plan": "Round 1 mid-cycle. Initiative order: Norn (13), Gibbering Mouther (12), Ghoul (11). Norn declared two attacks with longsword against the Ghoul: rolls 13 and 17. Against Ghoul AC 12, the 13 and 17 both hit. Awaiting damage rolls: 2 attacks 1d8+3 each. After damage, Gibbering Mouther acts, then Ghoul. Round remains 1.",
  "narration": "You lunge forward twice with your longsword swinging in a deadly arc against the ghoul's rotting form. Your first strike grazes its shoulder, the second cuts deeper into its side, tearing through moldering flesh and worn armor.\n\nBoth attacks find their mark! Roll 1d8 and add 3 for the damage of your first longsword strike, then roll again for the second.\n\nThe ghoul snarls in pain, baring yellowed teeth as the shadow of death looms closer. What damage do you deal with each hit?",
  "combat_round": 1,
  "actions": []
}

{
  "plan": "Round 1 mid-cycle. Norn's longsword attacks both hit. Damage rolls 8 and 1 from d8 plus +3 damage bonus make total damages 11 and 4 respectively. Total damage to Ghoul is 15. After damage is applied, Gibbering Mouther acts with multiattack followed by bites. Then Ghoul acts with bite and claws. Combat round remains 1 until all act.",
  "narration": "Your first swing cleaves deeply into the ghoul's putrid flesh, tearing a jagged wound that oozes dark ichor. The second strike barely nicks its side, but still leaves a shallow cut. The creature snarls, shaking with pain but still ravenous and ready to fight back.\n\nHold tight as the gibbering mouther churns toward you, its many eyes darting crazily and mouths opening wide to unleash a savage assault.",
  "combat_round": 1,
  "actions": [
    {
      "action": "updateEncounter",
      "parameters": {
        "encounterId": "E02-E1",
        "changes": "Ghoul takes 15 slashing damage from Norn's longsword attacks, HP reduced from 22 to 7."
      }
    }
  ]
}

{
  "plan": "Round 1 continuing. Initiative: Norn (13), Gibbering Mouther (12), Ghoul (11). Norn has completed attacks. Now Gibbering Mouther's turn with Multiattack (2 attacks: Bites). Using prerolled d20 18 for first attack and 12 for second. Proceed with attack rolls and damage rolls. Ghoul will act after Mouther attacks. Combat round will remain 1 until Ghoul acts.",
  "narration": "The gibbering mouther lurches forward, its grotesque mass of writhing mouths and staring eyes fixated on you with maddened hunger. It strikes out with its jagged, biting maws, attempting to rend your flesh with chaotic ferocity. The first snapping bite comes fast and true, claws scraping and teeth gnashing.\n\nBrace yourself for the second frenzied attack as the ghoul snarls in the darkness, eager to join the fray.",
  "combat_round": 1,
  "actions": []
}

{
  "plan": "Round 1 continuing. Gibbering Mouther made two bite attacks: first attack roll 18 vs AC 19 misses; second attack roll 12 vs AC 19 misses as well. No damage dealt to Norn. Ghoul now acts with two attacks: Bite and Claws. Using prerolled d20 18 and 18 for attacks against Norn. Proceed with attack rolls and damage rolls. Combat round 1 ends after Ghoul's turn.",
  "narration": "The gibbering mouther snaps its many jaws viciously towards you, but astonishingly, its frenzied bites fail to find purchase on your armored form. Its maddening gibbering fills the corridor, a cacophony of desperation and chaos, but the creature's ferocity does not translate into success.\n\nBefore you can catch your breath, the ghoul lunges forward with predatory hunger, jaws aiming to bite and claws ready to rake you. Its first attack comes swift and merciless, followed swiftly by a brutal clawing strike.",
  "combat_round": 1,
  "actions": []
}

{
  "plan": "Round 1 concludes. Both attacks by the Ghoul (bite and claws) roll 18 each, both less than Norn's AC of 19, so both attacks miss. No damage is dealt. All creatures have acted this round. Combat round increments to 2. Awaiting Norn's next action.",
  "narration": "The ghoul lunges forward with snarling ferocity, snapping its jaws wide and slashing with sharp claws. Yet your armor and reflexes serve you well, each attack narrowly missing as you dodge and parry with practiced skill. No harm comes to you this round as the twisted creature's fury frustrates against your defense.\n\nThe corridor seems to hold its breath as the dark denizens momentarily recoil, shrouding the moment in tense anticipation.\n\nRound 2 begins. The shadows twist once more, and the battle continues. What will you do next, Norn?",
  "combat_round": 2,
  "actions": [
    {
      "action": "updateCharacterInfo",
      "parameters": {
        "characterName": "Norn",
        "changes": "No damage taken, HP remains at 39."
      }
    }
  ]
}

{
  "plan": "Round 2 begins. Initiative order: Norn (13), Gibbering Mouther (12), Ghoul (11). Norn declares an attack with longsword against Ghoul, rolls 15 plus attack bonus 5, total 20, hitting Ghoul AC 12. Awaiting damage roll (1d8 + 3). After damage resolves, Gibbering Mouther acts then Ghoul. Combat round remains 2 until all creatures act.",
  "narration": "You shift your stance and bring your longsword down in a precise strike against the wounded ghoul. Your blade arcs through the stale prison air and finds its mark vividly, slicing into the creature’s flesh with a sharp rasp.\n\nRoll 1d8 plus 3 for the damage and let’s see how deeply your steel bites.",
  "combat_round": 2,
  "actions": []
}

{
  "plan": "Round 2 ongoing. Norn's attack hits Ghoul for 8 damage, killing it (HP 7 -> -1, status dead). Gibbering Mouther follows with two attacks, rolls 6 and 6 vs Norn's AC 19, both miss. No damage dealt to Norn. All creatures have acted this round; increment combat_round to 3. Prompt Norn for next action.",
  "narration": "You drive your longsword deeply into the ghoul's shrieking form, the blade cutting cleanly through rotten flesh. With a final, gurgling cry, the ghoul collapses, lifeless, onto the cold stone floor.\n\nThe gibbering mouther flails wildly next, its dozens of eyes darting madly as its multitude of jaws snap and bite at your armor. Despite its frantic attacks, none find a gap in your defenses, leaving you unscathed but wary of the creature's relentless madness.\n\nThe ghoul is dead, but the gibbering mouther remains a deadly threat. Round 3 begins. What will you do next, Norn?",
  "combat_round": 3,
  "actions": [
    {
      "action": "updateEncounter",
      "parameters": {
        "encounterId": "E02-E1",
        "changes": "Ghoul takes 8 slashing damage from Norn's longsword, HP reduced from 7 to -1, status changed to dead. Gibbering Mouther made two attacks against Norn, both missed."
      }
    }
  ]
}

{
  "plan": "Round 3 ongoing. Norn attacks Gibbering Mouther twice: first attack roll 19 is a crit, damage rolls 7 and 6 plus 3 = 16 total; second attack roll 17 hits, damage roll 5 plus 3 = 8 damage. Total damage to Gibbering Mouther is 24. After damage, Mouther acts with Multiattack (2 attacks) using prerolled d20 18 and 4 for attacks. Combat round remains 3 until Mouther acts.",
  "narration": "You strike with deadly precision at the gibbering mouther, your blade flashing in the dim light of the gaol's corridor. Your first attack finds a perfect opening, the critical hit slicing deep into the creature's writhing flesh. Your longsword bites viciously, leaving grievous wounds that momentarily still the creature's maddened gibbering.\n\nWithout missing a beat, you unleash your second strike, cutting into its mass and drawing more blood as it recoils with a guttural, almost human cry of pain. The monstrous aberration glares at you, bruised but far from defeated.\n\nPrepare yourself; the gibbering mouther lashes out in a furious cascade of bites.",
  "combat_round": 3,
  "actions": [
    {
      "action": "updateEncounter",
      "parameters": {
        "encounterId": "E02-E1",
        "changes": "Gibbering Mouther takes 24 slashing damage from Norn's longsword attacks, HP reduced from 67 to 43."
      }
    }
  ]
}

{
  "plan": "Round 3 continuing. Initiative order: Gibbering Mouther (12) acts now with Multiattack: two bite attacks. Attack rolls are 18 and 4. First attack roll 18 vs Norn AC 19 misses by 1; second attack roll 4 misses. No damage dealt. All creatures have acted in Round 3; increment combat_round to 4. Norn's turn next.",
  "narration": "The gibbering mouther lunges at you in a frenzy, dozens of spittle-flecked mouths snapping viciously. Its first bite snaps just short of your armor, a hair's breadth away from tearing into you. The second wild bite swipes uselessly through the air as you evade nimbly.\n\nDespite its madness and brutal attacks, it fails to land a strike against your steadfast defense.\n\nThe creature reels back, eyes rolling wildly, as the deadly dance continues. Your turn comes again, Norn. What do you do now?",
  "combat_round": 4,
  "actions": []
}

{
  "plan": "Round 4 ongoing. Norn attacks Gibbering Mouther twice with longsword. Attack rolls 15 and 16 both hit against AC 9. Damage rolls: first attack 6 + 3 = 9, second attack 7 + 3 = 10, total damage 19. After damage, Mouther acts with Multiattack using prerolled attack rolls 18 and 16. Combat round remains 4 until Mouther acts.",
  "narration": "Your longsword slices through the chaotic mass of mouths and eyes sprawling before you, cleaving deep into the gibbering mouther's twisted flesh. Your first strike draws a gush of dark ichor, the aberration shrieking in outrage.\n\nWithout pause, your second blow lands true again, carving bloody ribbons through its writhing form. The creature quivers with pain, yet its maddened eyes remain locked on you, fueled by relentless fury.\n\nBrace yourself — the gibbering mouther swings back with a furious volley of biting attacks.",
  "combat_round": 4,
  "actions": [
    {
      "action": "updateEncounter",
      "parameters": {
        "encounterId": "E02-E1",
        "changes": "Gibbering Mouther takes 19 slashing damage from Norn's longsword attacks, HP reduced from 43 to 24."
      }
    }
  ]
}

{
  "plan": "Round 4 continuing. Initiative order: Gibbering Mouther (12) acts now with Multiattack: two bite attacks. Attack rolls 18 and 16 against Norn's AC 19: first attack roll 18 misses by 1, second attack roll 16 misses. All attacks miss, no damage dealt. All creatures have acted this round; increment combat_round to 5. Norn's turn next.",
  "narration": "The gibbering mouther thrashes forward again, its spittle-flecked mouths snapping with fierce intent. Yet despite its relentless fury, each bite flies just shy of your armor, the sharp teeth scraping only air as you expertly evade.\n\nThe creature's maddened gibbering crescendos into a howl of frustration as it reels back into the shadows for a moment's respite.\n\nYour turn comes once more, Norn. What is your next move amidst these haunted halls?",
  "combat_round": 5,
  "actions": []
}

{
  "plan": "Round 5 ongoing. Norn attacks Gibbering Mouther twice with longsword. Norn's attacks hit with rolls 16 and 17 against Mouther AC 9. Damage total 18, reducing Mouther HP from 24 to 6. Mouther now attacks with Multiattack: two bites using attack rolls 5 and 5 against Norn AC 19, both miss. No damage to Norn. All creatures have acted this round; increment combat_round to 6.",
  "narration": "You deliver two powerful longsword strikes, slicing deeply into the gibbering mouther's chaotic mass. The creature shudders violently as blood and slime spray from the wounds, leaving it grievously injured but still thrashing.\n\nThe gibbering mouther responds with ferocious biting attacks, jaws snapping just wide of your armor, missing by mere inches. Though relentless, its teeth find only air as you expertly dodge the savage onslaught.\n\nThis brutal exchange leaves the creature wounded and panting, while you stand ready for what comes next.\n\nRound 6 begins. The gaol's shadows seem to pulse with anticipation. What will you do now, Norn?",
  "combat_round": 6,
  "actions": [
    {
      "action": "updateEncounter",
      "parameters": {
        "encounterId": "E02-E1",
        "changes": "Norn deals 18 slashing damage to Gibbering Mouther, reducing its HP from 24 to 6. Gibbering Mouther makes two bite attacks with attack rolls 5 and 5 against Norn's AC 19, both miss, no damage dealt."
      }
    }
  ]
}

{
  "plan": "Round 6 mid-cycle. Initiative order: Norn (13), Gibbering Mouther (12), Ghoul (11). Norn declared two longsword attacks against Gibbering Mouther; rolls 10 and 14. Both hits against Mouther AC 9. Await player damage rolls for both attacks (1d8 + 3 each). Combat round remains 6 until damage rolls and resolution. Mouther waits to act after Norn's attacks.",
  "narration": "Your longsword swings cut through the air, each strike landing solidly upon the gibbering mouther’s grotesque form. The creature recoils from your blows, its many eyes flickering with pain and frustration.\n\nNow, roll 1d8 and add 3 damage for your first hit. Then roll 1d8 plus 3 again for the second. Let’s see just how deeply your blade wounds this foul aberration.",
  "combat_round": 6,
  "actions": []
}

{
  "plan": "Round 6 resolution. Norn deals 8 and 7 slashing damage with longsword attacks, total 15 damage, reducing Gibbering Mouther from 6 HP to -9 HP, status changed to dead. All creatures have acted this round; combat ends. Advance combat_round to 7. Encounter concludes.",
  "narration": "Your longsword finds its mark with ruthless precision, each cut sinking deep into the gibbering mouther’s writhing flesh. The creature shudders violently as your final strike cleaves through its chaotic form, silencing its maddened gibbering forever.\n\nWith a wet splatter, the horrific aberration collapses into a lifeless heap, the corridor suddenly seeming colder and quieter without its ceaseless babbling.\n\nThe battle is over. Victory is yours, Norn.",
  "combat_round": 7,
  "actions": [
    {
      "action": "updateEncounter",
      "parameters": {
        "encounterId": "E02-E1",
        "changes": "Gibbering Mouther takes 15 slashing damage from Norn's longsword and dies, HP from 6 to -9, status dead."
      }
    },
    {
      "action": "exit",
      "parameters": {}
    }
  ]
}

Combat Summary: {
  "narration": "In the echoing, shadowed corridor of the Gaol, Norn faced a vicious combat against two monstrous foes: a ravenous ghoul and a maddened gibbering mouther. The encounter began with Norn striking twice at the ghoul, inflicting substantial wounds, and eventually slaying it with a decisive final blow. The gibbering mouther, a grotesque mass of eyes and mouths, relentlessly attacked with ferocious bites but failed to penetrate Norn's defenses. Through successive rounds, Norn unleashed precision longsword strikes, dealing critical and continuous damage, gradually reducing the mouther's vitality. Despite its frenzied multiattack attempts, the gibbering mouther could not overcome Norn's skillful evasion and steady assaults. Finally, two well-placed attacks ended the mouther’s maddened gibbering, collapsing it into a lifeless heap on the cold stone floor. The ghoul's corpse and the gibbering mouther's remains were left behind, marking the end of the deadly confrontation. For overcoming these perils, Norn was awarded a total of 650 experience points, reflecting the defeat of a CR 1 ghoul worth 200 XP and a CR 2 gibbering mouther worth 450 XP.",
  "combat_round": 6,
  "actions": [
    {
      "action": "updateCharacterInfo",
      "parameters": {
        "characterName": "Norn",
        "changes": "Alive with 39 HP and no conditions."
      }
    },
    {
      "action": "updateEncounter",
      "parameters": {
        "encounterId": "XXX",
        "changes": "Ghoul defeated and at 0 HP, gibbering mouther defeated and at 0 HP."
      }
    },
    {
      "action": "exit"
    }
  ]
}
